  "body": "<p>Every time I get the latest collection samples to work on catalog materials, I get goosebumps. Sometimes I dive right in and make a bunch of projects, while other times I just like to sit and stare at the new product. This time it was a mix of both pleasures. The funny thing is that when I first started putting together this post, I typed the title, \"Amy Tangerine dies\", and that just sounded much too morbid. But really, I did want to introduce <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one%20dies&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D65223%2F366860%2Ddie%2Ddies%2Dwafer%2FDetail\">the die set</a> that's new to American Crafts and part of the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Plus One collection</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4010895e3161fcd7.jpg?v=1782536907\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>It's great not only for card makers, but also scrapbookers and Project Lifers. The polaroid style frame is 3x4 inches and fits perfectly into a PL pocket. The embossed stitched details are my favorite part. And I love the little heart.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a9c1e89354489482.jpg?v=1782536910\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4819aa7a8a3cf301.jpg?v=1782536913\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Using the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/147243-counterpart-12x12-plus-one-amy-tangerine-paper/\">Counterpart paper</a> as the background, I layered on the goodness. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/146847-plus-one-amy-tangerine-accompany-large-clear-acrylic-stamp/\">\"Darling\"</a> was stamped with <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=mama%20elephant%20ocean&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D63388%2Fmama%2Delephant%2Dme%2Ddsh%2Doce%2Docean%2FDetail\">Mama Elephant ink in my new favorite color, Ocean</a>. I also used the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/147272-plus-one-amy-tangerine-teammate-embroidery-icon-stencil-kit/\">stitching template</a> for the house and made a stitched corner detail using half of the square.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1728e3ec8b7eaaed.jpg?v=1782536915\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aaac1877d63b9c85.jpg?v=1782536918\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/035f3199eb066f34.jpg?v=1782536921\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For more, shop <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Plus One at Simon Says Stamp</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
